Shoemaker, Omale Ojima aka OJ Best has died.
OJBest went viral after tweeting at Vice President Yemi Osinbajo about his products and making shoes for him.
His death was announced on his Twitter handle on Sunday evening.
The tweet read, “PAINFUL EXIT!! Call to Glory, the CEO of OJBest footwear is dead.”
